{"tid":2489744,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"物理系畢業生被控突圍理大暴動 早前被鄭念慈撤銷保釋 還柙51日後今於區院獲准保釋 湯博士及舍監任擔保人","createTime":"2021-04-15T06:36:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T06:54:25.000Z","uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"491726cc96dd236ae4f715955bb97c2df4141f9b","tid":2489744,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:36:48.000Z","msg":"前年「理大圍城」事件，一名就讀物理系的男生被指在科學館外攜有一個汽油彈，原被控一項管有攻擊性武器罪，直至今年2月尾，男生另被指從理大校園「突圍而出」，遭加控一項暴動罪，即時撤銷保釋，還柙至今已51日。現任職中大物理系活動主任的被告，今（15日）向區域法院申請保釋，法官李慶年聽取控辯雙方陳詞後，決定批出保釋。被告散庭後，向旁聽的朋友豎起姆指。<br />\n<br />\n被告由大律師黃瑞紅代表，獲准以3萬元保釋，中大物理系高級講師湯兆昇及宿舍舍監各以2萬元作人事擔保。被告在保釋期間不得離開香港、須交出旅遊證件包括BNO護照、每晚11時至翌日早上6時須守宵禁令、居於報稱住址及每周向警署報到4次。此外，其中一名擔保人須每天跟警方聯絡，確認被告仍在香港，若果擔保人與被告失去聯絡超過12小時，必須通知警方。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1082029\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1082029&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sDBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=07db8367\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1082029&h=a7643648\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1082029</a>"},{"pid":"d2f3884b84acf9ffefee85daaedcc6ac5c76a05d","tid":2489744,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:37:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db980ed696fad258322f4cf57d0ab7c0c1aa0ac5","tid":2489744,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T06:38:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c64d9b7d29f48efdecbcc9e0404e640f5191e3d","tid":2489744,"uid":14983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime